Ri referred to a joint statement issued by Kim Jong-un and Donald Trump during a premiere summit between a U.S. president and the North Korean leader in Singapore on June 12, where Kim pledged to make progress on a “denuclearization of the North Korean peninsula’s nuclear power plant.”
North Korea sought an official end to the 1950-1953 Korean War, but the United States declared that Pyongyang must first give up its nuclear weapons.
